Pitcairn Alternative Investment Fund Form D
The Pennsylvania-based Pitcairn Alternative Investment Fund L P filed form D because of $44.84 million offering. The date of first sale was 1996-03-29. The Limited Partnership raised $44.84 million. The offering is still open. The total offering amount was $44.84 million. The offering form was filed on 2015-10-16. Pitcairn Alternative Investment Fund L P’s clarification was: unspecified. 
 Pitcairn Alternative Investment Fund is based in Pennsylvania. The firm’s business is Pooled Investment Fund. The D form was signed by Richard E Borowy Executive Officer of General Partner. The company was incorporated more than five years ago. The filler’s address is: One Pitcairn Place, Suite 3000, 165 Township Line Road, Jenkintown, Pa, Pennsylvania, 19046. Dirk Junge is the related person in the form and it has address: One Pitcairn Place, Suite 3000, 165 Township Line Road, Jenkintown, Pa, Pennsylvania, 19046. Link to Pitcairn Alternative Investment Fund Filing: 000101154815000002.
Analysis of Pitcairn Alternative Investment Fund Offering
On average, companies in the Pooled Investment Fund sector, sell 37.80% investment fund interests. Pitcairn Alternative Investment Fund sold 100.00% of the offering. The average offering size is $24.76 million for companies in the Pooled Investment Fund industry sector. The minimum investment for Pitcairn Alternative Investment Fund ‘s private offering was $0.

