Learn More About Liquid Alternatives




















												Liquid Alternative Investments MAPS
											


The MAPS is designed to help investors understand the risks and potential reward of liquid alternatives.


















												Bringing Alternatives Within Reach
											


The GS Multi-Manager Alternatives Fund is a mutual fund that provides investors access to a diverse group of leading alternatives managers across a range of strategies. 

















												Seeking Consistent Returns Across All Market Environments
											


GS Absolute Return Multi-Asset Fund is a multi-asset class alternative investment portfolio that seeks to deliver consistent returns in all market environments through broad diversification and dynamic management. 

















